  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency eslint-plugin-jasmine to v2.9.1",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/tlvince/eslint-plugin-jasmine\">eslint-plugin-jasmine</a> from <code>v2.8.4</code> to <code>v2.9.1</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>tlvince/eslint-plugin-jasmine</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"291\">2.9.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tlvince/eslint-plugin-jasmine/commit/e79e5427170236227e08319bb18103c28823b618\"><code>e79e542</code></a> fix: readme links fix</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"290\">2.9.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tlvince/eslint-plugin-jasmine/commit/71bb9169eb30e68bbe5a665b3f808a4fea0ed4a9\"><code>71bb916</code></a> feat: new expect-matcher and expect-single-argument rules. depreacting valid-expect.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"286\">2.8.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tlvince/eslint-plugin-jasmine/commit/f3b3e8f70dc0af2395ee403f5d43c400ad7a552e\"><code>f3b3e8f</code></a> fix(new-line-before-expect): maintain expectation indentation</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"285\">2.8.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tlvince/eslint-plugin-jasmine/commit/c065a204b01ac88705c2d386691d0928f84101ee\"><code>c065a20</code></a> fix(no-global-setup): incorrectly triggered by describe.only</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
